Encoding: UTF-8
Package: hodfr
Type: Package
Title: Hands-on-Data-Frame for R
Version: 1.0-0
Date: 2017-11-01
Authors@R:
    c(person('Jamie','Lentin',email='lentinj@shuttlethread.com',role=c('aut','cre')))
Maintainer: Jamie Lentin <lentinj@shuttlethread.com>
Description:
    A Shiny widget that lets you add a dynamically-sized data.frame using
    Handsontable, a javascript spreadsheet. Templates let you choose bounds for
    the number and type of columns and rows.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0.0)
Imports:
    jsonlite,
    shiny
Suggests: 
BugReports: https://github.com/shuttlethread/hodfr/issues
LazyData: yes
